## Definition of Done

A task or backlog item is considered **done** when:

- Database tables are created according to the schema
- Relationships between entities are correctly implemented
- Seed data can be successfully inserted
- Backend application connects to the database without errors
- CRUD operations work as expected
- The database can be run using Docker
- Code is committed and pushed to GitHub
- Basic documentation or setup instructions are provided

